data.description: Are you looking for an updated, spacious, low maintenance home where convenience is paramount?  Welcome home to 384 Dalraida Road!  This home was just updated with all new LVP, tile and carpet.  Roof was replaced with architectural shingles in 2019 and both HVAC systems were completely replaced in 2022/2023 and all new vinyl, double paned windows with energy saving gas and tint were installed in 2016 .  Living room has vaulted ceiling and fireplace with gas logs.  Large master bedroom and bathroom are located on main level while two bedrooms and the second bath are located upstairs.  Bath to ceiling tiles have been replaced in showers in both bathrooms and new backsplash has been installed in the kitchen.  All that and you won't believe all the storage and the size of the closets in this home!  Within twenty minutes from here you can be to either military base, downtown, Eastchase, Prattville, Wetumpka and Millbrook.  This home is move in ready, call to see it today!
